Package ie.gmit.sw

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalculateCosine
    Calculate Cosine distance using the counted up dot product and magnitudes
    CalculateDotProductAndMagnitude
    Calculate the dot product and magnitudes of the maps to get the cosine distance for each file.
    FileParser
    Parse the files in the directory line by line into three word shingles and add them to the queue
    Index
    Index class - used to create an arraylist in the ShingleTaker class
    Poison
    Poison class - used to signify the end of a file for the ShingleTaker class
    PrintResults
    Option to print the results to file
    Processor
    Process documents selected by user
    QueryFileParser
    Parse the query file/url line by line into three word shingles and add them to a ConcurrentHashMap to be returned
    Runner
    Includes the main method to run the program Creates an instance of UI and calls display() Running time: O(1)
    ShingleTaker
    Callable thread class that takes words from the queue and adds them to a ConcurrentHashMap
    UI
    Displays and handles UI options for program
    Word
    Word class - used to add words to the BlockingQueue
